org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model

Class ConnectedTargetData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model.ConnectedTargetData

  • public class ConnectedTargetData
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains state and behavior of 'connected' DebugTargetImpl. Its inner implementation of DebugTargetImpl#State is for DebugTargetImpl only and is available externally only at construction. The class can be used only after setVmEmbedder(org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model.JavascriptVmEmbedder) was called. Listeners can be used from the beginning, but they are blocking until listenerBlock is unblocked which is done externally after setVmEmbedder(org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model.JavascriptVmEmbedder) is called.

    It corresponds to 'connected' state of target and post-terminated state.
